M|Pers|it|sy 1 is always running. Name the fast-thinking trap before recommending anything.
M|Pers|it|Biases are not flaws to fix — they are features of human cognition to work w/.
M|Pers|it|Confidence is not competence. Challenge overconfident recommendations regardless of source.
