M|CSE-|Thes|
M|CSE-|tx|\| Bias \| How it appears in CSE \| Correction \|
M|CSE-|tx|\|---\|---\|---\|
M|CSE-|tx|\| **Availability bias** \| "This is trending → therefore our audience wants it" \| Check if the tn data comes from a matched tier (our size), not viral accounts \|
M|CSE-|| **|what % of this cr's similar posts underperformed? \|
M|CSE-|tx|\| **Overconfidence in growth hypothesis** \| Growth hypothesis predicts specific % improvement w/o base rate \| Flag if no comparable historical data supports the range \|
M|CSE-|tx|\| **Anchoring on cr metrics** \| Using a large cr's engagement rate as the target benchmark \| Re-anchor to the vt's own Stage 0/1/2 benchmarks \|
M|CSE-|| **|is the tn ≥3 weeks old and still accelerating, or a spike? \|
M|CSE-|| **|does the cr gap exist even if we ignore our preferred narrative? \|
M|CSE-|| **|gain vs loss** \| Hooks written as loss aversion when gain framing wld be more authentic \| tst both frames — loss aversion converts but damages br trust over time \|
